metadata.description: Comprehensive audit of all ore fragment files for W1/W2 classification

classification_key.w1: Pure Densworld material - suitable for mnemonic images. Contains only Densworld geography, characters, and concepts.
classification_key.w2: Real-world references - contains Alton/Illinois, Walmart, real people, missionaries, evangelical Christianity, etc.
classification_key.ambiguous: Contains real-world elements but with fantastical/transformative qualities that could work as W1, or unclear classification.

w2_themes: Alton, Illinois and Mississippi River geography
